# Contributor: Chris Schwaab
pkgname=ats-lang-anairiats
pkgver=0.2.6
pkgrel=1
pkgdesc="A dependantly typed ML style programming language."
arch=('i686' 'x86_64')
url="http://www.ats-lang.org/"
license=('GPL3')
depends=('gmp')
provides=('ats-lang')
source=("http://voxel.dl.sourceforge.net/sourceforge/ats-lang/$pkgname-$pkgver.tar.gz")
md5sums=('da949088549ca6e56e504d8c0be0817e')

build() {
	cd "$pkgname-$pkgver"

	export ATSHOME="$(readlink -e `pwd`)"
	export ATSHOMERELOC=ATS-$pkgver
	./configure --prefix=/usr || return 1
        make -j1 all || return 1
        make DESTDIR=$pkgdir install || return 1
}
